                    <h1>Sacrilegious chic is the trendiest way to protest</h1>

                      <h2 class="deck">The Gen Z fashion trend uses sacred Christian imagery as a form of sociopolitical critique. </h2>


                    <div class="credits">
                        <div class="author">
    <span>
      By <span class="credit_name"><a href="/contributor/sandra-song">Sandra Song</a></span>
  </div>


<div class="posted">
  <div>
    April 19, 2024
  </div>
</div>

                    </div>

